<TEXTAREA NAME="Text" COLS="60" ROWS="6" WRAP="VIRTUAL" >Please read this ソニックチーム.

 I know its rude talking in english here, but please take your time reading this, but it seems you guys are focused on the japanese BBS rather than the english BBS.

 I know I could of emailed you, but it seems that I never get replys back. So I decided to post it here.

 We all love your games ソニックチーム, and we know you guys are really busy. I would like you if any chance, update the english section of this site. It would make us extreamly happy if you updated the english site just like the excellent update design you did to the japanese section. Americans think that you do not care about Americans, and I personally do not think that. I personally think you love everyone just about equally.

 Another problem on the english section is the BBS. I know you all heard of &quot;Falco&quot; on the BBS. He caused alot of problems, but it is not only him that is causing problems, theres alot of other people. I think you should check the English BBS of the bbs more than the Japanese BBS, because to me, it looks like this BBS has no problems whats so ever. It seems you are only banning people who are flooding. There IS people who are breaking the &quot;Terms of Usage&quot; rule. You should take an eye on the BBS.

You can read my topic I posted on the SONICTEAM BBS from 2 months ago here:

http://www2.sega.co.jp/bbs/article/s/sonic/40/xvfqjh/xvfqjh.html

We all love you SONICTEAM, and we will love you more if you do what I asked you to do! And we espcially love you Mr.Naka

I am really hyped up about Sonic Heroes!
</TEXTAREA></TD>

